{"about_the_game":"A novel logic puzzle game that sharpens thinking skills.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThat satisfying feeling that comes from solving a puzzle! Presenting the novel Japanese logic puzzle game that's been attracting attention from around the world!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFind your way to the solution, deducing unknown lengths and areas from known lengths and areas.<br />\r\nAll you need is the &quot;length x breadth = area&quot; formula for calculating the area of a rectangle!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u25c6Solve any problem as long as you hone your thinking skills!<br />\r\nFind your way to the solution hidden in each problem!<br />\r\nEven problems that may seem difficult at a glance do not use decimals or fractions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCAUTION: Challenge yourself without judging by appearance alone!<br />\r\nTo prevent the solving of problems simply based on appearance, the lengths and areas written may differ from the actual proportions in the diagram.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n*The problems included are the same as those in the smartphone version of Area Maze.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Clear level 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3063450/3de13792cee55f38af28f6c6c6f7780dd501c199.jpg"},{"name":"Clear level 4","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3063450/77e2f34a044bb76f898c1f0071f65e93671febbf.jpg"},{"name":"Clear level 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3063450/25cfbce37b44d53bb2cb880e8d21deee0202a3fb.jpg"},{"name":"Clear level 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3063450/4739babc5d9bccc0dda0a1e84c7d31b5a512169b.jpg"},{"name":"Clear level 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3063450/667da7c5b7f61689385da48b36bebe257bae9237.jpg"}],"total":5},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063450/page_bg_generat